Features
•Syntax Error Detection: Identifies syntax errors in Python code.
•Logical Error Detection: Detects logical issues in the code.
•Best Practices: Provides suggestions for improving code readability and maintainability.
•Optimizations: Offers recommendations for optimizing code performance.
•User-Friendly Interface: Built with Gradio, making it easy to use for developers of all levels.

How It Works
1.Code Input: Users paste their Python code into the Gradio interface.
2.AI Analysis: The code is analyzed using Google Gemini AI and NLP tools.
3.Feedback: The tool provides detailed feedback on syntax errors, logical issues, best practices, and optimizations.
4.Improved Code: Suggestions for improved code are provided, along with explanations.
